OL,5, A footballer who suffered major brain  
OL,6, injuries after being punched will be   
OL,7, allowed out of hospital for Christmas, 
OL,8, his family have said.                  
OL,10,FDanny Hodgson, 26 and originally from  
OL,11,FCleator Moor in Cumbria, was left in a 
OL,12,Fcoma by an unprovoked attack in        
OL,13,FSeptember in Perth, Australia.         
OL,15,FHis family said having him out of      
OL,16,Fhospital was the "perfect gift".       
OL,18,FA 17-year-old boy is due to be         
OL,19,Fsentenced in January after admitting   
OL,20,Fcausing grievous bodily harm.          
